    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="一-node-js环境配置"><a href="#一-node-js环境配置" class="headerlink" title="一 node.js环境配置"></a>一 node.js环境配置</h1><span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="node-js下载"><a href="#node-js下载" class="headerlink" title="node.js下载"></a>node.js下载</h2><h2 id="node-js安装"><a href="#node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="node.js安装"></a>node.js安装</h2><h2 id="node-js检测"><a href="#node-js检测" class="headerlink" title="node.js检测"></a>node.js检测</h2><h1 id="二-git-安装"><a href="#二-git-安装" class="headerlink" title="二  git 安装"></a>二  git 安装</h1><h1 id="三-github设置"><a href="#三-github设置" class="headerlink" title="三 github设置"></a>三 github设置</h1><h2 id="账号注册"><a href="#账号注册" class="headerlink" title="账号注册"></a>账号注册</h2><h2 id="github仓库设置"><a href="#github仓库设置" class="headerlink" title="github仓库设置"></a>github仓库设置</h2><h1 id="四-hexo-命令"><a href="#四-hexo-命令" class="headerlink" title="四 hexo 命令"></a>四 hexo 命令</h1><h2 id="hexo-init"><a href="#hexo-init" class="headerlink" title="hexo init"></a>hexo init</h2><p><code>hexo init </code> </p>
<p>命令用于初始化本地文件夹为网站的根目录。</p>
<p><code>hexo init [floder]</code></p>
<p>[folder]可选参数，用以指定初始化目录的路径，若无指定则默认为当前目录。</p>
<h2 id="hexo-new"><a href="#hexo-new" class="headerlink" title="hexo new"></a>hexo new</h2><h2 id="hexo-generation"><a href="#hexo-generation" class="headerlink" title="hexo generation"></a>hexo generation</h2><h2 id="hexo-server"><a href="#hexo-server" class="headerlink" title="hexo server"></a>hexo server</h2><h2 id="hexo-deploy"><a href="#hexo-deploy" class="headerlink" title="hexo deploy"></a>hexo deploy</h2><h2 id="hexo-clean"><a href="#hexo-clean" class="headerlink" title="hexo clean"></a>hexo clean</h2>]]></content>
